PEOPLE ex rel. DOTY v. BOARD OF POLICE OF YONKERS. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. December 1, 1893.) Action by the people on the relation of Doty against the board of police of Yonkers.

Argued before BARNARD, P. J., and DYKMAN and PRATT, JJ.

No opinion. Writ of certiorari quashed and judgment affirmed for failure to submit according to stipulation.
